#: ../../../release_details/9.5/relative-temporal-array-operator.md:1
msgid "Relative Mode for vtkTemporalArrayOperatorFilter"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/relative-temporal-array-operator.md:3
msgid ""
"The `vtkTemporalArrayOperatorFilter` now has a `RelativeMode`, where it uses "
"`UPDATE_TIME_STEP` time as first value alongside to a `TimeStepShift` "
"shifted value, instead of two static time steps."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/relative-temporal-array-operator.md:5
msgid "Behavior Breaking Change"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/relative-temporal-array-operator.md:7
msgid ""
"This filter was inconsistent on which input mesh and arrays were forwarded "
"to output: Composite data used first input, while non composite used second. "
"The forwarded data is now the one given by `FirstTimeStepIndex` when "
"`RelativeMode` is off or by `UPDATE_TIME_STEP` otherwise, as Composite used "
"to do."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/relative-temporal-array-operator.md:10
msgid "Build Breaking Change"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/relative-temporal-array-operator.md:12
msgid ""
"The protected variable members where moved to private. From inherited "
"classes, please use Getter/Setter instead."
msgstr ""
